{"tid":719234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"絕境的王!世界的王!宇宙級第6球 美斯帶阿根廷上岸!","createTime":"2018-06-27T09:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T16:09:08.000Z","uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e50899a05e08e53303ebbff4568f1828e3dfd872","tid":719234,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/2018/06/27/038dee6263ca42e2908d1ae57d3b2174.jpeg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F038dee6263ca42e2908d1ae57d3b2174.jpeg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=86812029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\t<br />\n如何用好美斯？對陣冰島，桑保利讓美斯在每次進攻中都觸球，這極大加重了對美斯的體能損耗。對陣克羅地亞，桑保利又讓美斯在前場當個幌子牽製後衛，阿根廷隊長全場只有一次射門。在對陣奈及利亞的生死戰中，桑保利終於想明白了。讓隊友承擔組織責任，讓美斯更多出現下對方禁區內﹗阿根廷2-1戰勝奈及利亞晉級16強，美斯是首功﹗\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n在前兩場比賽中，巴內加幾乎沒怎么得到過機會。對陣奈及利亞，桑保利決定讓巴內加首發。在阿根廷目前中場體系下，巴內加是少有的組織核心型球員。開場僅僅14分鐘，巴內加就送出了頭班生涯最重要的助攻之一。\t<br />\n\t<br />\n在中場，巴內加送出一記落點極為精準的挑傳。美斯快速前插，他在禁區弧內完成了停球。美斯的動作銜接極為連貫，他用大腿將球停住，然後左腳向右前方縱向一趟。透過這個連停帶趟的動作，美斯將球帶到了後衛無法伸腳攔截的防守盲區。\t<br />\n\t<br />\n作為足球史上最著名的金左腳之一，美斯通常情況下喜歡依靠左腳完成技術動作。但這一次，美斯選擇右腳大力推射。美斯的這次射門，勢大力沉極為精準，皮球直掛球門右上死角。\t<br />\n\t<br />\n這個進球，是美斯世界杯生涯第六個進球，同時也是他本屆世界杯中打進的第一球。這個進球，還是本屆世界杯中第100個進球。破門之後，美斯罕見地顯得極為激動。這個進球，也直接改變了阿根廷隊的命運﹗"},{"pid":"825e44891f42ab0e146e90853beb58258ce0ea9e","tid":719234,"uid":23536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:15:45.000Z","msg":"55⋯⋯"},{"pid":"9447a82a9b1a46e876c1718f8de72cb6c114e416","tid":719234,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a691bafe379d0421c615d7baadbcd83f47907677","tid":719234,"uid":186181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4be4f0b3224fcb9e9d9de0a3cea41a8a1d6504","tid":719234,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"慢鏡睇果球真心勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0549ab9b62a5b2aab187a76caac289253d96321","tid":719234,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"王者歸來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/argentina.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10895bca9f5e323ffb811aa769e9fc627f4c63a","tid":719234,"uid":18674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"都唔知係咪假膠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n贏個一場出咁多篇飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1f7955d012f560c09c4e82e60d9a1634b4698b","tid":719234,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"美斯 = GOD<br />\n牙朗 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d1016d39253da05be7af8b735cbd9ed08803eb","tid":719234,"uid":25345,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ab1f7955d012f560c09c4e82e60d9a1634b4698b","tid":719234,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"美斯 = GOD<br />\n牙朗 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"DOG"},{"pid":"aef223edba25627cc09ac61c6b986e2e0fd8cbb7","tid":719234,"uid":4180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9b4be4f0b3224fcb9e9d9de0a3cea41a8a1d6504","tid":719234,"uid":80035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"慢鏡睇果球真心勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac